### 13.3 Resetting VLA Kafka topic offset

Stop **all data-engine** pods first.

| Goal | Topic | Group |
|------|--------|--------|
| **Metadata + VLA conversion** (calculated data + unarchived `NULL`/`FAILED`) | `vla-va-call-denormalized-calculated` | `cg-vla-va-call-denormalized-calculated-de-dumper` |
| **VLA conversion only** (unarchived `NULL`/`FAILED`) | `vla-conversion-pipeline` | `cg-vla-conversion-pipeline-de-conversion-processing` |

Substitute topic/group into the same reset patterns as §13.1.

`--to-datetime`:

```bash
/root/ameyo/kafka/bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server <kafka_broker_host:9091> \
  --group <group-id> --reset-offsets --to-datetime 2024-01-01T00:00:00.000 \
  --topic <topic-name>

/root/ameyo/kafka/bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server <kafka_broker_host:9091> \
  --group <group-id> --reset-offsets --to-datetime 2024-01-01T00:00:00.000 \
  --topic <topic-name> --execute
```

`--by-duration`:

```bash
/root/ameyo/kafka/bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server <kafka_broker_host:9091> \
  --group <group_name> --reset-offsets --by-duration PT0H10M0S --topic <topic-name>

/root/ameyo/kafka/bin/kafka-consumer-groups.sh --bootstrap-server <kafka_broker_host:9091> \
  --group <group_name> --reset-offsets --by-duration PT0H10M0S --topic <topic-name> --execute
```

