## 14. Contact Center — Kafka Streams & KSQL (Superset / analytics)

**By Aadit Bhojgi** (internal doc). Available **Kafka streams** for the **Contact Center** platform and usage notes for **customer-specific** **KSQL** pipelines.

These streams hold **structured, real-time** event data for calls, agents, sessions, monitoring, and user activity — sources for **real-time analytics, dashboards, reports, and alerts**.

Confirm stream/table names in your cluster (`SHOW STREAMS;` / `SHOW TABLES;`).

