### 16.1 PromQL — consumer lag (Kafka Exporter / compatible metrics)

**Lag by partition — alert when lag &gt; 20** (example: topic `ExternalLegEvent_TN_MH`, group `hermix-group-leg-tn-mh`):

```promql
sum by (consumergroup, partition) (
  max by (consumergroup, topic, partition) (
    kafka_consumergroup_lag{
      topic="ExternalLegEvent_TN_MH",
      consumergroup="hermix-group-leg-tn-mh"
    }
  )
) > 20
```

**Lag rolled up by topic** (same topic/group filters):

```promql
sum by (consumergroup, topic) (
  max by (consumergroup, topic, partition) (
    kafka_consumergroup_lag{
      topic="ExternalLegEvent_TN_MH",
      consumergroup="hermix-group-leg-tn-mh"
    }
  )
)
```

